PRIVACY POLICY
Biashara Boost Mobile App, 
by Arrianah Investments Kenya

At Biashara Boost, sponsored by Arrianah Investments Kenya, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard the information you provide when using our mobile application.
1. Information We Collect
   - Personal Information: When you register for Biashara Boost, we collect your name and phone number. This information is used for communication purposes and customization of your experience within the app.
   - Business Details and Plans: To facilitate the decision-making process for awarding grants, we collect information about your business details and plan. This may include the nature of your business, the proposed use of the grant, and other relevant details.
2. Use of Information
   - Personal Information: Your name and phone number are used solely for communication purposes related to the Biashara Boost app. We may also use this information to customize your experience within the app, such as sending personalized notifications or updates.
   - Business Details and Plans: The information you provide about your business is used to evaluate your eligibility for a startup grant. This includes assessing the viability and potential impact of your business plan.
3. Information Sharing
   - We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.
   - Your business details and plans are only shared internally with our team members involved in the grant selection process.
4. Data Security
   - We take appropriate measures to protect your personal information and ensure its security. This includes encryption of data transmission, regular system updates, and restricted access to your information within our organization.
5. Consent
   - By using the Biashara Boost mobile app and providing your personal and business information, you consent to the collection, use, and sharing of this information as outlined in this Privacy Policy.
6. Changes to Privacy Policy
   - We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting on the Biashara Boost app. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any updates.

If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy or the handling of your personal information, 
Please contact us at ariannahtech@gmail.com. 
Thank you for choosing Biashara Boost for your entrepreneurial journey!
